Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.77,0:00:06.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這身衣服和你很相稱
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.19,0:00:08.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常性感
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.27,0:00:11.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真壁…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.68,0:00:19.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天的櫻井令我燃起了沉睡於心中的熱情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.76,0:00:22.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我一直都沒察覺到呢
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.70,0:00:27.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我迷上櫻井你了 要和我交往嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.59,0:00:32.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 你突然這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.95,0:00:37.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小傻瓜 愛總是突如其來的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.72,0:00:39.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回答我Yes
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.06,0:00:41.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.33,0:00:44.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 我
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.35,0:00:48.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我已經有喜歡的人了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.37,0:00:52.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.57,0:00:54.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.41,0:00:57.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.58,0:01:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然把我甩掉 你可別後悔
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.24,0:01:38.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是時候讓橘知道你對他的心意了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.25,0:01:53.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 女孩們
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.87,0:01:55.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和我去玩玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.27,0:02:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他這麼說哦 響
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.23,0:02:03.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是在向我們搭訕嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.25,0:02:05.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是失禮了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.50,0:02:22.94,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}邂逅的那一瞬
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.77,0:02:29.55,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}察覺到的朦朧情感
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.08,0:02:37.25,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}直至已化為確信的今日
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.32,0:02:41.90,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}那份感覺仍否在你心中？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.19,0:02:43.59,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}全因有你
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:46.67,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Check my soul Check my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.76,0:02:50.79,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}心湖泛起陣陣漣漪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.07,0:02:56.08,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}此刻與你一同邁步
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.13,0:02:59.22,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Check my soul Check my soul
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.39,0:03:03.20,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}聆聽心聲
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.60,0:03:04.69,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}前行吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.15,0:03:08.83,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}去感受內心的律動
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.84,0:03:13.99,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}宛如夢幻的時間流淌著
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.01,0:03:21.79,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}渴望凝望你雙眸中的真實
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.68,0:03:25.87,SS+OPCN1,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\be1}Check my soul Check my soul
